title: FC Spartak Tuymazy
text:
FC Spartak Tuymazy () is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> team from <a href="Tuymazy">Tuymazy</a>.
Club history.
The club was founded in 1967 and played on amateur levels. It was licensed for the third-tier Russian <a href="Russian%20Professional%20Football%20League">FNL 2</a> for the 2021–22 season.
